{"tid":2131510,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"國際關注港押後立會選舉 美促如期舉行","createTime":"2020-07-30T02:16:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-31T10:45:31.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"3a25623061e57843ad72e6b9e28339b54af3c676","tid":2131510,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T02:16:46.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200730/GG5RT7JEEME3TST4PVOF3RTTDU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200730%2FGG5RT7JEEME3TST4PVOF3RTTDU%2F&d=6fRpkjTAYTcnGOSNIV5vhPFndj8FUwf2P%2BvTNEmbS2k%3D&h=12abca76\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200730%2FGG5RT7JEEME3TST4PVOF3RTTDU%2F&h=6ac210ea\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200730/GG5RT7JEEME3TST4PVOF3RTTDU/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n國際關注港押後立會選舉 美促如期舉行<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】正當9月立法會選舉提名期即將結束，日前傳出港府已決定押後選舉一年，並提請人大常委延長現屆立法會議員任期一年。消息引起國際社會關注，美國國務卿蓬佩奧（Mike Pompeo）及澳洲外長佩恩（Marise Payne） 發表聯合聲明，表明支持9月立法會選舉，以有公信力方式選出代表，外媒形容兩人是促如期舉行選舉。英國外相藍韜文（Dominic Raab）及歐盟亦表態會密切關注9月立法會選舉情況。<br />\n<br />\n傳媒昨繼續引述消息，。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n押後立法會選舉的消息引起國際社會高度關注，。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n英國外相藍韜文前日與中國外長王毅通話後，。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n正身處海外的前香港眾志成員羅冠聰在facebook發文，認為9月立法會選舉影響國際局勢，所以港府延遲選舉一事要提請人大常委決定，反映事件不止是香港內部事務，對國際局勢也有一觸即發的影響。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/urOu9fuynNYgxm41Tdbbpxm_FL4=/1158x772/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/7TJCD3W6LZKARJWAG4PW5BXKUM.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FurOu9fuynNYgxm41Tdbbpxm_FL4%3D%2F1158x772%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F7TJCD3W6LZKARJWAG4PW5BXKUM.gif&h=77471fc8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n美國國務卿蓬佩奧及澳洲外長佩恩發表聯合聲明，支持港人通過自由及有公信力的選舉，如期選出立法會代表。路透社<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n黃之鋒憂親共派永續議席<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：聯合國：國安非限制人權理據<br />\n<br />\n參選新界東立法會選舉的前香港眾志秘書長黃之鋒在facebook發文，批評政府以押後選舉一年為名，「萬世取消選舉為實」，擔心先例一開，日後每屆議員任期亦要由人大釋法，「恐怕香港將與台灣威權時期一樣，正式邁進『萬年國代2.0』時代，容許親共派毋須透過選舉下永續議席」。<br />\n<br />\n行政會議成員湯家驊在電台節目稱，對立法會選舉延後決定不知情，認。。。。。。。。。"},{"pid":"94c708cad6d09d9ea718313f8bcf0f1518f8b4bd","tid":2131510,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T04:51:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fba7b4dd21042b928cc1f01dca6144b5d2dd8575","tid":2131510,"uid":3149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T04:59:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60a10d81aff3d54bc97b93f128d8cc1b6a6a89e4","tid":2131510,"uid":32148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T10:40:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://mobile.twitter.com/ChadPergram/status/1288857607655116802\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmobile.twitter.com%2FChadPergram%2Fstatus%2F1288857607655116802&d=6fRpkjTAYTcnGOSNIV5vhPFndj8FUwf2P%2BvTNEmbS2k%3D&h=7a384ecd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmobile.twitter.com%2FChadPergram%2Fstatus%2F1288857607655116802&h=0790faaa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://mobile.twitter.com/ChadPergram/status/1288857607655116802</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢件肥垃圾就算把啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bdfefe2f0fa99e8d9eb9eb8b78314a4ffe23f9dc","tid":2131510,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T10:45:31.000Z","msg":"行政會議成員湯家驊在電台節目稱，對立法會選舉延後決定不知情，認。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n同你衰11一樣？"}]}